These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, onion, watermelon, orange
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, skydiving, card-games, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, rowing, parkour, surfing
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating orange is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person eating orange##6
 5. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
 8. the person eating onion is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
 9. the person eating raspberry is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
10. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
11. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##8
12. the person eating onion is in an even position##4
13. the person eating orange is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
14. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | raspberry         | orange     | watermelon     | onion         |
| Hobby   | skydiving | video-games    | card-games     | traveling |
| Sport   | tennis       | rowing | surfing | parkour       |

