.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, fisherman, engineer, accountant
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, lacrosse, climbing, sailing
 1. the engineer is not to the right of the accountant##8
 2. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fisherman##1
 5. the paramedic is not the person drinking tea##6
 6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the paramedic##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | tea          | mirinda      | hot-chocolate      | lemonade   |
| Job        | engineer     | paramedic | fisherman | accountant      |
| Sport      | sailing | lacrosse    | water-polo  | climbing |

