.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, fishing, video-games, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, hip-hop, folk, electronic
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, trike, bus, taxi
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is not the fan of jazz##6
 6. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the fan of electronic##8
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | video-games  | fishing | rock-climbing | writing |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | jazz      | electronic | folk        |
| Transport     | quad-bike | bus       | taxi    | trike     |

