.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, comedy, adventure, animation
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, blues, reggae, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, mexican, pakistani, dutch
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 2. the mexican is not to the left of the fan of blues##8
 3. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
 4. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the mexican##8
 6. the pakistani is not to the right of the person watching animation movies##8
 7. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
 8. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 9. the spanish is on the left of the pakistani##1
10. the person watching animation movies is the pakistani##1
11. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | animation | comedy    | adventure |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | blues     | rock   | indie     |
| Nationality   | spanish | pakistani   | mexican | dutch    |

