The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, mystery, superhero, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, parkour, skiing, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
 8. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | traveling       | board-games | camping  | chess    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero       | time-travel    | mystery | documentary    |
