.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, cabbage, lime, strawberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, family, drama, musical
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, polish, mexican, canadian
 1. the person eating lime is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8
 2. the person watching musical movies is not the polish##6
 3. the mexican is somewhere between the person eating cabbage and the person watching musical movies##7
 4. the polish is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
 6. the mexican is the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the canadian is between the person eating pepper and the mexican##2
 9. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
10. the person eating lime is not to the right of the person eating strawberry##8
11. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | cabbage      | lime      | strawberry | pepper |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | spy    | musical | family     |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | mexican | canadian  | polish |

