There 4 different types of food: strawberry, onion, kale, spinach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, salsa, gospel, d&b
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person eating kale##7
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
4. the fan of gospel is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
5. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person eating strawberry is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
7. the person eating spinach is the fan of salsa##1
8. the person eating spinach is somewhere between the fan of d&b and the person drinking almond-milk##7
9. the person eating spinach is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk     | sprite | juice  | water |
| Food          | onion | spinach   | strawberry | kale |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | salsa   | d&b      | gospel      |

