.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, camping, cooking, filmmaking
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, canadian, chinese, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, roller, jet-ski
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
 2. the indian is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the chinese##7
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 4. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the turkish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 7. the indian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 8. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
10. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
11. the turkish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
13. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting    | cooking | filmmaking | camping    |
| Nationality   | chinese  | indian    | turkish      | canadian |
| Transport     | bus | bike          | jet-ski      | roller       |

