 1. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 2. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person watching horror movies##6
 4. the person watching epic movies is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
 5. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the person watching horror movies##8
 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 7. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
10. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
11. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
12. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
13. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
14. the person driving the motorbike is not the person watching scientific movies##6

