5. the pakistani is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the spanish##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is parkour##7
8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
9. the person who's sport is cricket is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian     | spanish  | mexican |
| Pet           | rat      | horse        | bird   | dog |
| Sport         | parkour  | cricket | sailing | weightlifting       |

 